"<strong>ERROR</strong>: the server presented a certificate which is from an "
"unknown authority!"
msgstr ""
"<strong>ERROR</strong>: ¡el servidor presentó un certificado proveniente de "
"una autoridad desconocida!"

#: web/diag/radius_tests.php:351
